Class DiaryList

  • java.lang.Object
    • DiaryList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<DiaryList>, java.lang.Iterable<Diary>

    public class DiaryList
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<DiaryList>, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Iterable<Diary>
    A special list which should only contain Diaries with the same name. A component of a multiset-like structure, see DiaryTree.java.
    Author:
    AC12001 17/18 group 2
